### CIEPointer {#af2eda74e6b5621b79b29d812e95118b1}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>const uint64&#95;t llvm::dwarf::FDE::CIEPointer</>}>
The following fields are defined in section 6.4.1 of the DWARFv3 standard.

Note that <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf/cie">CIE</a> pointers in EH FDEs, unlike DWARF FDEs, contain relative offsets to the linked CIEs. See the following link for more info: <a href="https://refspecs.linuxfoundation.org/LSB_5.0.0/LSB-Core-generic/LSB-Core-generic/ehframechpt.html">https://refspecs.linuxfoundation.org/LSB&#95;5.0.0/LSB-Core-generic/LSB-Core-generic/ehframechpt.html</a>
